---
/**
 * Services Section
 *
 * Showcases the four core competencies with expandable details
 */

import Container from '../Container.astro';
import Section from '../Section.astro';
import Accordion from '../Accordion.astro';
---

<Section id="services" spacing="xl" background="light">
  <Container>
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Core Competencies</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Strategic guidance and hands-on expertise across four key areas to help your business thrive
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="competencies-list">
      <Accordion id="operations-finance" title="Operations & Financial Management">
        <svg slot="icon" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/>
          <rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/>
          <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"/>
          <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"/>
        </svg>
        <p>
          <strong>Build the operational and financial foundation</strong> that transforms chaos into clarity—from organizational design to CFO-level financial leadership, all without the full-time executive cost.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're scaling rapidly, navigating a downturn, or raising capital, we help you establish the systems, processes, and financial rigor that enable strategic decision-making instead of reactive firefighting.
        </p>
        <p><strong>What We Deliver:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Organizational design and operating cadences that replace chaos with strategic leadership, plus project delivery systems that transform stalled initiatives into completed work</li>
          <li>Finance function buildouts—reporting systems, cash tracking, financial models, and investor-ready materials that support successful fundraising and sustainable growth</li>
          <li>Executive dashboards integrating operational, sales, and financial data for real-time visibility and faster decision-making on pricing, promotions, and resource allocation</li>
          <li>Cost optimization and treasury management—identifying expense reductions while protecting revenue, improving working capital and cash flow, and implementing hedging programs to stabilize costs</li>
        </ul>
      </Accordion>

      <Accordion id="technology" title="Technology Consulting & Solutions">
        <svg slot="icon" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/>
          <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
          <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
        </svg>
        <p>
          <strong>Bridge the gap between business needs and technical solutions</strong> with computer science expertise from Stanford University and hands-on development experience.
        </p>
        <p>
          From building MVPs to implementing enterprise systems, we help startups, nonprofits, and established companies turn data into action and technology into competitive advantage.
        </p>
        <p><strong>What We Deliver:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Production web applications and custom platforms—view our complete portfolio of projects at <a href="https://scratchspace.dev/" target="_blank" rel="me noopener noreferrer">scratchspace.dev</a>, including Inevitable Ethereum (educational platform), Prompt Library (AI tools), and AI Context System (developer productivity)</li>
          <li>Custom websites, MVPs, and internal systems for organizations from early-stage startups to established companies—translating your business requirements into scalable technical solutions</li>
          <li>Data gathering and analytics infrastructure that transforms raw data into actionable insights—dashboard creation, automated reporting, and predictive modeling</li>
          <li>Strategic technology guidance on stack selection, system architecture, workflow automation (Zapier, Make, n8n), and digital transformation initiatives aligned with your business outcomes</li>
        </ul>
      </Accordion>

      <Accordion id="blockchain" title="Blockchain & Digital Asset Technologies">
        <svg slot="icon" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
          <rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
          <rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
          <rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
        </svg>
        <p>
          <strong>Navigate the blockchain landscape</strong> with deep technical expertise and industry connections built since 2020—from protocol-level understanding to practical implementation and strategic positioning.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're exploring blockchain solutions, building in web3, or need technical education and research, we bring hands-on experience as a DAO contributor, protocol consultant, and creator of leading Ethereum educational resources.
        </p>
        <p><strong>What We Deliver:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Blockchain implementation consulting and technical advisory—from evaluating use cases to architecting solutions, with experience advising startups through major protocols like Lido</li>
          <li>Protocol research, technical education, and content creation—creator of <a href="https://inevitableeth.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Inevitable Ethereum</a>, a premier resource for Ethereum technical education</li>
          <li>DAO participation and governance consulting—hands-on experience contributing to decentralized organizations and navigating web3 organizational structures</li>
          <li>Industry positioning and network access—deeply integrated into the professional blockchain community with connections across the ecosystem, plus active podcasting (<a href="https://sigtheory.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Signal Theory</a>)</li>
        </ul>
      </Accordion>

      <Accordion id="podcasting" title="Podcasting">
        <svg slot="icon" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/>
          <path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/>
          <line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="22"/>
        </svg>
        <p>
          <strong>Launch and grow your podcast</strong> with professional production services backed by experience as a host, producer, and editor across independent and media company settings.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you need contract work, strategic consulting, or a bespoke partnership, we'll help you create a podcast that resonates with your audience. Recent launches include <a href="https://strangewater.xyz/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Strange Water</a>, <a href="https://rexkirshner.com/expansion" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Expansion</a>, and <a href="https://sigtheory.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Signal Theory</a>.
        </p>
        <p><strong>What We Deliver:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Full podcast launches from concept to distribution—spanning crypto/web3, personal development, technology, and business topics with all aspects handled end-to-end</li>
          <li>Complete production services including hosting, audio engineering, editing, post-production, and quality control—delivering broadcast-quality content on time and on budget</li>
          <li>Podcast strategy tailored to your business goals, audience growth, and content sustainability—from show positioning and episode planning to guest booking and promotional campaigns</li>
          <li>Flexible engagement models including contract production work, strategic consulting, or fully bespoke partnerships to bring your podcast vision to life</li>
        </ul>
      </Accordion>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>

<style>
  .competencies-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .competencies-list {
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
